							.box--subtitle Permit applications
							.box--text New permit applications set record in&nbsp;2016. Year-to-year variation is&nbsp;high and the 2017 year saw significantly reduced volume of&nbsp;applications. To&nbsp;meet mayor&rsquo;s goal in&nbsp;housing production, permit filings volume needs to&nbsp;stay high consistently for several years.

